### MENTALMASS Backend API Tests
### Install REST Client extension in VS Code to run these directly

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Register New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Register Another User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Smith",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "secure456"
}

### Register - Missing Fields (Error Test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### Register - Invalid Email (Error Test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Invalid Email User",
  "email": "notanemail",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Register - Password Too Short (Error Test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Weak Password User",
  "email": "weak@example.com",
  "password": "123"
}

### Register - Duplicate Email (Error Test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Duplicate User",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password456"
}

### Login - Success
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login - Valid User 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "secure456"
}

### Login - Wrong Password (Error Test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### Login - User Not Found (Error Test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nonexistent@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login - Missing Fields (Error Test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com"
}

### Get All Users (Testing)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/users

### Notes:
### - Server must be running: npm run server
### - Each request can be tested individually
### - VS Code REST Client: https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client
### - Or use Postman to import these requests
